('66a94e5e-fd8a-5c4e-97e5-712f9fdb4ba9', 'c1ced4b0-ac55-44e0-8fe6-f95bb0aef02a', 'The cat is hiding ___ the two boxes in the garage.', '貓咪躲在車庫裡的兩個箱子之間。', 'between', 'among', 'amidst', 'beside', 'tween 表示「兩者」', '兩者之間用 between'),
